{"tid":1648340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非戰線 ver 0.1之 召喚campaign高手","createTime":"2019-10-12T07:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:17:06.000Z","uid":94613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9f92b45b28f7d343b268e3dab162d3eb22ea4248","tid":1648340,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:10:52.000Z","msg":"細佬我上個post<br />\n大家已跌入黑警勝利方程式<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1645295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1645295</a><br />\n係上個post入面大家都好似認同可以搞一個<br />\n #boycottchinabrand challenge(正式名稱有待確定）<br />\n暫時細佬我諗到可行方法係可以參考其他challenge做法<br />\n例如：ice bucket challenge <br />\n點解要搞一個呢個野出黎呢 <br />\n原因係要比中國知道世界唔接受中國呢個管治手法<br />\n方法係由打擊中國經濟入手<br />\n係上個post都講左幾個boycott 方法<br />\n其中 boycott china brand好似比較容易做到<br />\n所以暫時會向呢方面入手<br />\n同埋要集合中國brand list（搞哂國企同民企定只搞國企？）<br />\n例如 ticktok 華為 暴雪  小米 騰訊 <br />\n理由其實有好多 我會由2樓開始比理由去boycott中國brand<br />\n但由於細佬我真係唔係campaign高手<br />\n所以而家開放比做開campaign ge巴打去提議點樣去實行呢個方案<br />\n或者騎劫都冇問題<br />\n只要達到最尾目的：世界同香港connect去一齊反中國式打壓<br />\n就冇問題<br />\n以下開放討論個challenge形式 手法 或者成個theme<br />\nSORRY FOR1999"},{"pid":"ac858b9bf006ee7cc8af6209555477d450b64bb7","tid":1648340,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:11:11.000Z","msg":"偷data 運番去中國<br />\n<a href=\"http://culture.affinitymagazine.us/tik-tok-is-scamming-people-stealing-information/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fculture.affinitymagazine.us%2Ftik-tok-is-scamming-people-stealing-information%2F&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=fa1e7e56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://culture.affinitymagazine.us/tik-tok-is-scamming-people-stealing-information/</a><br />\n2. 打壓言論自由<br />\ne.g. 近排暴雪事件 / nba<br />\n3. 唔專重知識產權<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/380801/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%96%E9%96%93%E6%97%97%E8%89%A6%E5%BA%97%E4%BC%BC%E8%B6%B3apple-store-ceo-%E5%BE%88%E